sequenceDiagram
    participant Domain Event (e.g. Checkout)
    participant Analytics Event Handler
    participant PostgreSQL Rollup Table
    participant Celery Beat (Nightly)

    Domain Event (e.g. Checkout)->>Analytics Event Handler: OrderCompletedEvent
    Analytics Event Handler->>PostgreSQL Rollup Table: UPDATE gross = gross + X WHERE date = today
    
    Note right of PostgreSQL Rollup Table: Lock-free F() expression increment
    
    Analytics Event Handler->>Redis Cache: bump_cache_version()
    
    Note over Celery Beat (Nightly), PostgreSQL Rollup Table: 2:00 AM Nightly Reconciliation
    Celery Beat (Nightly)->>PostgreSQL Rollup Table: Recalculate yesterday from raw Order tables
    Celery Beat (Nightly)->>PostgreSQL Rollup Table: Overwrite yesterday's row to heal drift
